{"id":612320549,"lang":"javascript","lang_name":"JavaScript","time":"1 year, 8 months","timestamp":1641236613,"status":11,"status_display":"Wrong Answer","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/612320549/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Add Strings","memory":"N/A","code":"/**\n * @param {string} num1\n * @param {string} num2\n * @return {string}\n */\nvar addStrings = function(num1, num2) {\n    let long = num1.length >= num2.length ? num1 : num2\n    let short = num1.length < num2.length ? num1 : num2\n    short = \"0\".repeat(long.length - short.length) + short\n    \n    let sum = \"\"\n    let carry = 0\n    for (let i = long.length - 1; i >= 0; i -= 1) {\n        const add = (parseInt(long[i]) + parseInt(short[i])) % 10\n        carry = Math.floor((parseInt(long[i]) + parseInt(short[i])) / 10)\n        sum = (carry + add).toString() + sum\n    }\n    if (carry > 0) sum = carry.toString() + sum\n    return sum\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"add-strings","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
